room_title: Escape room "Central Bank" by Fox in a Box Orange County in Orange County
room_description: You are a group of well-informed thieves. It has come to your attention that the general manager of Central Bank has a stash of diamonds hidden in his office. Under the cloak of night, you sneaked into the bank and reached the office of the manager's assistant, from there you deactivated the alarm, but it will sound off in exactly one hour. If you get to the diamonds in time, you will be rich beyond your wildest dreams. Fail, and you will end your career behind bars.
